  "description": "The image showcases a large pine cone lying on a white surface. The cone is elongated and cylindrical in shape, exhibiting a rich, textured surface composed of numerous overlapping scales. These scales are predominantly shades of olive green and brown, with some displaying darker, almost blackened tips. The base of the cone appears broken or cut, revealing the wood beneath. The scales are tightly packed, creating a complex and organic pattern. The white background provides a stark contrast, emphasizing the cone\u2019s details and texture.",
